<component name="NrrdJoin" category="Filters">
  <overview>
    <authors>
      <author>Martin Cole</author>
    </authors>
    <summary>module interface for nrrdJoin function.</summary>
    <description>
      <p>The number of input nrrds vary.  Attempt to join all the
nrrds along the user specified axis, and output that NrrdData. This
module can be used to create sets of data.  Join the sets along the
tuple axis, to create such a nrrd.  Or you can use this module like
unu_join <slink
path="http://www.cs.utah.edu/~gk/teem/unrrdu/join.html"></slink></p>
    </description>
    <examplesr>Teem/nets/test/field_set.net</examplesr>
  </overview>
  <io>
    <inputs lastportdynamic="yes">
      <port>
        <name>Nrrds</name>
	<datatype>Teem::Nrrd</datatype>
      </port>
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
      <port>
        <name>JoinedNrrd</name>
	<datatype>Teem::Nrrd</datatype>
      </port>
    </outputs>
  </io>
  <testing>
  </testing>
</component>
